latestIgtvVideos.title: SAFFRON(kesar) HOMEMADE FACE PACK
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Guys! 
So here it is, the Saffron Homemade Face Pack. 
INGREDIENTS : 
1. Saffron, Milk, Oil, 1 bread, sugar

DIRECTIONS TO USE : 
1. Soak saffron in 1tsp overnight in water.
2. Add 1tsp milk, 1tsp sugar & 1tsp oil (of your choice) and mix
3. Take 1 bread, add the breadcrumbs in the mixture.
4. Mix all, & apply the paste all over your face.
5. Wait for 15mins. Wash & soak with towel. 
I have been trying this remedy from the past 1 month & it really did make a difference on my skin. 
Do try it ! 😃

latestIgtvVideos.title: HOME-MADE COFFEE FACE PACK!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
INGREDIENTS : 
Coffee, Milk, Honey, Cotton, Cocoa Powder

DIRECTIONS: 
1. Take 1Tsp milk
2. Add 1 Tsp Cocoa Powder 
3. Add 2 Tsp coffee powder & 1/2 tsp honey. Mix well. 
4. Using a cotton ball, apply the paste all over the paste. • Coffee contains healthy antioxidants which helps in whitening the skin. It also helps shrinking the pores, decreases fine lines. Its a must try pack!😃
